      <talk_question mid="22"><![CDATA[<html>$Suitable Place$<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(The scent of the pond wafts from the sparkling water and the breeze blows gently, mixed with the smell of flowers. This is just the right sunny spot near the pond.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
