   <talk_paragraph index="n2958_her_ghost-3" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2958_her_ghost-3-a" mid="85" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>… What?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="25"><![CDATA[<html>$Soran's Ghost$<BR><FONT color=#a82424>My love Daegwang!</FONT> Now we're together forever. Huh?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2958_her_ghost-3-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2958_her_ghost-3-b" mid="86" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Uh… Who are you? Hmm, might you be Soran?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="26"><![CDATA[<html>$Soran$<BR>What, why no Daegwang? Where is he?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2958_her_ghost-3-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2958_her_ghost-3-c" mid="87" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Um... Are you looking for your husband?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="27"><![CDATA[<html>$Soran's Ghost$<BR>I'm sure I told him to…<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(After looking around, the ghost grimaces.)</FONT><BR>What, did he order someone else to do it? He made you do this? Well, that's just great.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2958_her_ghost-3-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2958_her_ghost-3-d" mid="88" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html><FONT color=#7e12d2>(You ordered the man who has nothing but love for you to do something dangerous...)</FONT></html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="28"><![CDATA[<html>$Soran's Ghost$<BR>Of course! I was going to take that old man with me because the <FONT color=#a82424>afterlife</FONT> is too lonely, and he goes and makes you do it?!<BR>How could he be so shameless? He told me that he'd love me forever, yet he wanted someone else to do it for his own safety?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2958_her_ghost-3-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2958_her_ghost-3-e" mid="89" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>You're not taking me with you, are you?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_answer link_index="n2958_her_ghost-3-e" mid="90" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Holds the sword firmly without saying a word)</FONT></html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="29"><![CDATA[<html>$Soran's Ghost$<BR>Well, he's been like that all his life. Tsk, how am I going deal with my loneliness in the afterlife?<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(The ghost looks this way.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2958_her_ghost-3-e" image="QW_187.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2958_her_ghost-3-f" mid="91" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Well, I heard there's a <FONT color=#a82424>secret exit</FONT> in <FONT color=#086171>Red Lotus Palace</FONT> that only you know about?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="30"><![CDATA[<html>$Soran's Ghost$<BR>Don't worry. I'm not so awful as to kidnap the person who buried me in such a pretty, sunny place.<BR>But I'll give you a little reward. Do you want me to tell you some of the best restaurants on Main Street?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2958_her_ghost-3-f" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2958_her_ghost-3-g" mid="92" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>… It was a lie?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="31"><![CDATA[<html>$Soran's Ghost$<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Soran's ghost clucks her tongue as if exasperated.)</FONT><BR>Tsk! I made him promise to cut that out, but now he's spreading the lie to random strangers?]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2958_her_ghost-3-g" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2958_her_ghost-3-h" mid="93" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Oh, come on, that's not cool.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="32"><![CDATA[<html>$Soran's Ghost$<BR>You're quite naive, though you certainly don't look it.<BR>I was just a Red Lotus Palace attendant. How would I know that? Pfft, what a sneaky old man.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2958_her_ghost-3-h" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2958_her_ghost-3-i" mid="94" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>This is it, then?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="33"><![CDATA[<html>$Soran's Ghost$<BR>Let me give you a piece of advice.<BR>You won't receive adequate payment from him. Be careful.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2958_her_ghost-3-i" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2958_her_ghost-3-j" mid="95" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html><FONT color=#7e12d2>(What a mess…)</FONT></html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="34"><![CDATA[<html>$Soran's Ghost$<BR>What do you want me to do? You should go complain to the crook!<BR>Oh, woe is me! I thought we'd be together for eternity in this beautiful place.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2958_her_ghost-3-j" image="QW_134.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2958_her_ghost-4" mid="96" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Well, I can't thank you enough for your useless advice.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="35"><![CDATA[<html>$Soran's Ghost$<BR>Well, I'm going to take a stroll around <FONT color=#a82424>Red Lotus Palace Garden</FONT>.<BR>Okay young man, I'll be wishing you luck from the afterlife.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2958_her_ghost-4" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="36"><![CDATA[<html>$Soran's Ghost$<BR>Anyway, I'm going to take a stroll through <FONT color=#a82424>Red Lotus Palace Garden</FONT>.<BR>Okay young man, I'll wish you luck from the afterlife.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2957_oldman-4" image="QS_Default.dds" itemindex="400713" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2957_oldman-4-a" mid="97" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Yes, I buried it deep inside <FONT color=#a82424>Red Lotus Palace Garden</FONT> by the pond.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="37"><![CDATA[<html>$Daegwang$<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Daegwang is surprised to see you and laughs awkwardly.)</FONT><BR>Hahaha, look who it is! My hero! Did you give Soran a proper burial?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2957_oldman-4-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2957_oldman-4-b" mid="98" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>What about the secret exit?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="38"><![CDATA[<html>$Daegwang$<BR>Thank you! You are a lifesaver!<BR>I will live the rest of my life praying for your good fortune. Well, then...</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2957_oldman-4-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2957_oldman-4-c" mid="99" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html><FONT color=#7e12d2>(No way am I going to let you off that easy.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="39"><![CDATA[<html>$Daegwang$<BR>Hmm? Oh, that thing! Yeah, I was supposed to tell you. Hahahaha...<BR>Of course I have to tell you! I wrote down what Soran said... Where is it...? I'll have to bring it.<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(He clearly is looking for a chance to escape.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2957_oldman-4-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2957_oldman-4-d" mid="100" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Let's see if we can trick him into telling the truth.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="40"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>Actually, your wife appeared at the pond.<BR>She looked very surprised and disappointed. She asked me where you were.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2957_oldman-4-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2957_oldman-4-e" mid="101" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>I should scare him.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_answer link_index="n2957_oldman-4-g" mid="102" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>I should bait him.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="41"><![CDATA[<html>$Daegwang$<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Daegwang's eyes shoot open.)</FONT><BR>What? So-Soran appeared? As a ghost?!</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2957_oldman-4-e" image="QW_134.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2957_oldman-4-f" mid="104" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Daegwang looks scared.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="42"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>"My dream was to die with my beloved,<BR>so come to </FONT><FONT color=#a82424>Red Lotus Palace Garden</FONT><FONT color=#662500>. If you don't come, I'll visit you every night as a vengeful spirit."<BR>That's what she said!</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2957_oldman-4-f" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2957_oldman-4-i" mid="105" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Pfft! Swindler.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="43"><![CDATA[<html>$Daegwang$<BR>Ugh! Get me out of this mess! A vengeful spirit... Ugh, no matter how much I loved Soran, this can't be!<BR>I gotta get away from here! Help! I don't want to die!</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2957_oldman-4-g" image="QW_Hell_23.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2957_oldman-4-h" mid="106" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Daegwang's face becomes greedy.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="44"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>"I asked him to bury me here because I left a </FONT><FONT color=#a82424> precious treasure</FONT><FONT color=#662500> here for my beloved, but he didn't come to claim it.<BR>It's too bad... I'll tell him the location of the treasure when he comes."<BR>That's what she said!</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2957_oldman-4-h" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2957_oldman-4-i" mid="107" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Wow, he suddenly has courage now that treasure's involved?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="45"><![CDATA[<html>$Daegwang$<BR>Oh, my… Thank you so much!<BR>I've got to get going now. Oh, don't worry about the pay. I'll give you some treasure when I get back from the garden! Just trust me!</html>]]></talk_question>
